PN,38401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778699495
OL,3,CVoters with disabilities sound alarm
OL,4,Cover lack of interest in accessibility
OL,6,FA visually impaired man in Jersey says
OL,7,Fit is "disappointing" that just six
OL,8,Fout of the 92 election candidates have
OL,9,Fpromised in their manifestos to take
OL,10,Faction on improving accessibility.
OL,12,FExplaining his frustrations ahead of
OL,13,Fthe General Election on Sunday 7 June,
OL,14,FJohannes Martinson says: "I think the
OL,15,Fcandidates need a serious talk to
OL,16,Funderstand what it means to take care
OL,17,Fof people with disabilities."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778699495
OL,3,CVoters with disabilities sound alarm
OL,4,Cover lack of interest in accessibility
OL,6,FLuke du Val, who has cerebral palsy,
OL,7,Fagrees, stating he has not yet "felt
OL,8,Flistened to or represented by
OL,9,Fpoliticians".
OL,11,FJohannes and his wife Estelle moved to
OL,12,Fthe island from South Africa seven
OL,13,Fyears ago and say that while they are
OL,14,F"very happy in Jersey", getting from
OL,15,Fplace to place can be extremely
OL,16,Fchallenging.
OL,18,FHe explains: "I always have to figure
OL,19,Fout before I go anywhere, 'Is it
OL,20,Faccessible, where can I park?'.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778699495
OL,3,CVoters with disabilities sound alarm
OL,4,Cover lack of interest in accessibility
OL,6,F"I'm not just thinking, 'I want to go
OL,7,Fto that place'; there are a lot of
OL,8,Fconsiderations going on beforehand.
OL,10,F"People say it costs money to refit a
OL,11,Fbuilding, but if it were made
OL,12,Faccessible from the start, then that
OL,13,Fplace would already be accessible.
OL,15,F"It's an attitude, people need to
OL,16,Fthink about it from the start, it's
OL,17,Fmuch easier and cheaper that way."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778699495
OL,3,CVoters with disabilities sound alarm
OL,4,Cover lack of interest in accessibility
OL,6,FJohannes continues: "I think the
OL,7,Fcandidates need a serious talk to
OL,8,Funderstand what it means to take care
OL,9,Fof people with disabilities.
OL,11,F"Currently, we have ministers looking
OL,12,Fto improve life for the youth, which
OL,13,Fis good, but we also need someone with
OL,14,Fa title or a minister looking at life
OL,15,Ffor people with disabilities.
OL,17,F"For example, someone saying, 'All
OL,18,Fsidewalks need to be flat, need to be
OL,19,Fthis size, etc' so there is clear
OL,20,Fguidance."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778699495
OL,3,CVoters with disabilities sound alarm
OL,4,Cover lack of interest in accessibility
OL,6,FAs Jersey goes to the polls and with
OL,7,FSenators back on the ballot, ITV
OL,8,FChannel's Jess Dunsdon and Luke
OL,9,FKeohane break down the key election
OL,10,Fissues alongside expert guests. Listen
OL,11,Fto Jersey Votes wherever you get your
OL,12,Fpodcasts or watch on ITVX, and YouTube
OL,13,Fbelow, with new episodes each
OL,14,FThursday...
OL,16,FEstelle says the lack of understanding
OL,17,Fof islanders with disabilities is
OL,18,Fupsetting.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778699495
OL,3,CVoters with disabilities sound alarm
OL,4,Cover lack of interest in accessibility
OL,6,FShe explains: "I see his struggles and
OL,7,Fthey do frustrate me, such as
OL,8,Finformation not being accessible.
OL,10,F"My husband and a lot of people living
OL,11,Fwith a disability really treasure
OL,12,Findependence. Johannes doesn't always
OL,13,Fwant to ask me for help.
OL,15,F"We were looking at the different
OL,16,Fmanifestos and were just struck by how
OL,17,Flittle is actually being said for
OL,18,Fpeople living with a disability.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778699495
OL,3,CVoters with disabilities sound alarm
OL,4,Cover lack of interest in accessibility
OL,6,F"One of the key things that would make
OL,7,Fa difference in their lives is
OL,8,Fattitude; it's not expensive
OL,9,Fadaptations.
OL,11,F"It is really just that people want
OL,12,Fthe willingness to ask, 'Does this
OL,13,Fwork for you?'
OL,15,F"It should be designed into the way we
OL,16,Fdo things rather than as an
OL,17,Fafterthought."
OL,19,FMeanwhile, Luke says he has always
OL,20,Frelied upon the third sector for
OL,21,Fsupport rather than politicians.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778699495
OL,3,CVoters with disabilities sound alarm
OL,4,Cover lack of interest in accessibility
OL,6,FHe adds: "It is only this year that I
OL,7,Fam actively considering voting, it's
OL,8,Fjust about reading all the manifestos
OL,9,Fand thinking who might have my best
OL,10,Finterest in mind, but I can't say that
OL,11,FI have felt so far the particular
OL,12,Fissue of both being a disabled person
OL,13,Fand a young person considering my
OL,14,Ffuture has been touched on really.
OL,16,F"I feel quite disconnected from the
OL,17,Fworld of politics and how it can make
OL,18,Fa difference to my life.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778699495
OL,3,CVoters with disabilities sound alarm
OL,4,Cover lack of interest in accessibility
OL,6,F"Up until now, I have felt that it has
OL,7,Fbeen up to charities, such as Enable,
OL,8,Fto make sure that, from a disability
OL,9,Fperspective in particular, I have a
OL,10,Fvoice.
OL,12,F"I haven't felt listened to or
OL,13,Frepresented by politicians up to this
OL,14,Fpoint."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778699495
OL,3,CVoters with disabilities sound alarm
OL,4,Cover lack of interest in accessibility
OL,6,FHighlighting what needs improving,
OL,7,FLuke believes: "Fairness and equality
OL,8,Ffor everyone, really. As a
OL,9,Fcontributing member of society, I
OL,10,Fthink it's important that we all feel
OL,11,Fas important, respected and seen as
OL,12,Feveryone else, and sometimes that is
OL,13,Fnot the case.
OL,15,F"I think it is important that success
OL,16,Fis the same for everyone, that I can
OL,17,Fenter the building the same way as
OL,18,Feveryone else, rather than going
OL,19,Faround the back.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778699495
OL,3,CVoters with disabilities sound alarm
OL,4,Cover lack of interest in accessibility
OL,6,F"It's about feeling equal and all on
OL,7,Fthe same footing, and we're all
OL,8,Fwanting to vote to make a difference
OL,9,Fto make all of our lives better.
OL,11,F"Politicians just need to be more
OL,12,Fwilling to not only hear what young
OL,13,Fand disabled people have to say but
OL,14,Falso to be their voice in rooms and
OL,15,Fconversations that they have access
OL,16,Fto, because it can be tiring when I
OL,17,Fhave to advocate for people like me."
OL,19,FMeanwhile, voters have been assured
OL,20,Fthat this year's election will be more
OL,21,Faccessible.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778699495
OL,3,CVoters with disabilities sound alarm
OL,4,Cover lack of interest in accessibility
OL,6,FJenny O'Brien, Head of Digital and
OL,7,FPublic Engagement at the Jersey States
OL,8,FAssembly, explains: "Postal voting is
OL,9,Fnow open to everyone, so that is one
OL,10,Fway to give people access to voting.
OL,12,F"We have done audits of all the
OL,13,Fpolling stations.
OL,15,F"Information about whether there is a
OL,16,Fdisabled parking bay and wheelchair
OL,17,Faccess, whether the doors are
OL,18,Fautomatic, all the kind of information
OL,19,Fthat people would need getting in and
OL,20,Fout of a polling station, will all be
OL,21,Flisted online ahead of the election.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778699495
OL,3,CVoters with disabilities sound alarm
OL,4,Cover lack of interest in accessibility
OL,6,F"When it comes to the polling station,
OL,7,Fwe will have special magnifiers and
OL,8,Flights to help people who might have
OL,9,Fvisual impairments, which will assist
OL,10,Fthem.
OL,12,F"At the senatorial hustings, the final
OL,13,Fone, we will have a British Sign
OL,14,FLanguage interpreter who will be there
OL,15,Fto support people who need that
OL,16,Fassistance.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G13/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778699496
OL,3,CVoters with disabilities sound alarm
OL,4,Cover lack of interest in accessibility
OL,6,F"We are also working really closely
OL,7,Fwith charities that have specialist
OL,8,Fknowledge around specific
OL,9,Fdisabilities, and so we are doing what
OL,10,Fwe can to take their advice to provide
OL,11,Fas much support as we can to make sure
OL,12,Fnobody is unable to vote this year."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G14/14
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
